Class PhotoListController

java.lang.Object
controller.PhotoListController
All Implemented Interfaces:
ErrorMessage, Logout
public class PhotoListController extends Object implements ErrorMessage, Logout
This controller controls the PhotoList.fxml as well as the PhotoDisplay.fxml files. This controller implements the ErrorMessage and Logout interfaces.
